Launcher - Class in com.stefanski.booksearch

Application Launcher
Allowed parameters format: parameter: title - search for this "title" parameter: multipart title - search for this "multipart title" parameter: -t title - use previous search results of "title" parameter: -t multipart title - use previous search results of "multipart title"
Example: java Launcher -t java - use previous saved search for "java" title java Launcher sql for beginers - search for "sql for beginners" title
loggerInit() - Static method in class com.stefanski.booksearch.Launcher
